= SDL_GetWindowID =
Use this function to get the numeric ID of a window, for logging purposes.


== Syntax ==
```c++
Uint32 SDL_GetWindowID(SDL_Window* window)
```

== Function Parameters ==
{|
|'''window'''
|the SDL_Window to query
|}

== Return Value ==
Returns the ID of the window.

